genresAdvancedInfo.name: rap salvadoreno
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Rap salvadoreno is a genre of rap music that originated in El Salvador. It is characterized by its raw and gritty style, often featuring socially conscious lyrics that touch on topics such as poverty, violence, and political corruption. The beats are typically heavy and bass-driven, with influences from traditional Salvadoran music and hip hop.
